name: Logisuite
tag_list: logistics-software, third-party-logistics, 3pl, nvocc, freight-forwarding-software, inventory-control, supply-chain-management, purchase-order-management
overview:
Logisuite is a software development company that designs and sell software for the logistics & transportation industry. Logisuite offers a complete portfolio of solutions including Inventory Control, Supply-Chain Management, Third-Party Logistics (3PL), Freight Forwarding System, Import System, Domestics Freight, Pickup & Delivery, Purchase Order Management and more. All Operations system and fully integrated with Logisuite Financials a complete accounting system design for this specific industry.

Logisuite also offers Logisuite Information Portal a complete online cargo tracking system that is completed integrated into the operation systems letting customers see real-time tracking information of their cargo and inventory. Customers also have the ability of view and print documents and pictures of their cargo from the web. Company agents have the ability to enter and modify cargo status events and proof of delivery (POD) information.

Logisuite is constantly adopting and incorporating the latest technologies into their system. The newest version of their software includes support for SQL Server 2008 the most recent database software from Microsoft. SQL Server 2008 provides the highest levels of security, support for millions of transactions, reliability, and scalability for business-critical applications.
